  3.6364764743118906`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"aabaa99f-a835-4111-9a60-\
e9fff6a10676"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In many cases, the numerical function (",
 StyleBox[ButtonBox["NSolve",
  BaseStyle->"Link",
  ButtonData->"paclet:ref/NSolve"],
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 ") can be faster than the symbolic function (",
 StyleBox["N[Solve[...", "MR"],
 ")."
