  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " and ",
 StyleBox[ButtonBox["FindMinimum",
  BaseStyle->"Link",
  ButtonData->"paclet:ref/FindMinimum"],
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " are functions that search for local extrema from a given point."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.608646508378971*^9, 3.608646540804213*^9}, {
   3.608646685576689*^9, 3.6086467748126116`*^9}, {3.608646829990128*^9, 
