   3.60864755288041*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"11e59bae-e9e3-458f-bbfb-\
b16cea3b2b1e"],

Cell["\<\
Built into the Wolfram Language are state-of-the-art linear and nonlinear \
fitting capabilities, conveniently accessed with models given directly in \
symbolic form. The Wolfram Language also supports interpolating functions \
that can immediately be used throughout the system to efficiently represent \
approximate numerical functions. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.5634432739533243`*^9, 3.563443307726144*^9}, {
   3.563443790117324*^9, 3.563443851173542*^9}, 3.563878270898696*^9, 
   3.5642173120417776`*^9, {3.5681427419525647`*^9, 3.568142786432816*^9}, {
